Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.18,0:00:20.99,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.99,0:00:23.61,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了令人忧伤的纯粹简单
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.12,0:00:26.95,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在夕阳西下时的道场一角
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.22,0:00:29.65,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挥洒着汗水练习刀法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:33.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.08,0:00:35.59,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了引人发笑的满腔热情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.17,0:00:38.89,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}「我也是有梦想的啊」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.20,0:00:41.79,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}像傻瓜般这样大声叫喊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:46.08,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.68,0:00:49.10,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}朝阳东升的话
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.73,0:00:52.07,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你会在喧闹的街上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.52,0:00:55.12,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}拼命奔跑着吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:58.18,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}若是你所在的街道上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.51,0:01:01.03,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}深夜降临的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.71,0:01:04.09,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}你会穿过宽阔的大道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.53,0:01:06.13,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}在河滩边诉说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:09.00,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}是这样吧 我的挚友
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.69,0:01:16.60,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}挚友啊 挚友啊 在你身上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.60,0:01:19.26,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}我看到了一颗赤子之心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.68,0:01:22.49,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}想必你正守护着重要的性命
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.61,0:01:25.49,mushibugyo_OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}脸上透露着决心吧
